 size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><strong>International Cargo Spedition</strong></strong></font></strong></font><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"> possesses the largest, most advanced car shipping         and airplanes fleet in the industry. Car carriers of all sizes and types         are available to meet your specific requirements. A multitude of options         are available to meet your specific needs&#8212;you may wish to have your         car delivered directly to your door or you may wish to pick your car up         at one of over 85 terminal locations across the globe. Most of our vehicles         ship onboard an enclosed transport to ensure maximum protection for your         vehicle during its journey. (<a href="moto_pack.php">View example on how         the motorcycles are packed</a>).</font></p>      <p align="justify"><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br>        Technology moves almost as fast as </font><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><strong>International Cargo Spedition</strong></strong></font></strong></font></font></strong></font></strong></font><strong></strong></font></strong></font><strong><font color="#333333" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"></font></strong><font color="#333333" size="2"></font></font><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"> does. Satellite tracking provided by Qualcomm         allows all of </font><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><strong>International Cargo Spedition</strong></strong></font></strong></font><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">         customers to log on to the web site to get the exact location of their         car transport vehicle en route. <br>        For the past years, <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><strong>International Cargo Spedition</strong></strong></font></strong></font></font></strong></font></strong></font><strong></strong></font></strong></font><strong><font color="#333333" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"></font></strong><font color="#333333" size="2"></font></font><font color="#333333"></font> has been the auto transport company of choice. With the most experience         in the industry and the highest quality trucks and training for its employees, </font><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><strong>International Cargo Spedition</strong></strong></font></strong></font></font></strong></font></strong></font> will         make your vehicle Transaction as simple and worry-free as is possible.</font><br>        <br>      </p></td> 